History[]

31 January 2020: 3 stations opened (Woodlands North - Woodlands South) TE1 - TE3

28 August 2021: 6 stations opened (Springleaf - Caldecott) TE4 - TE9

13 November 2022: 11 stations opened except Mount Pleasant and Marina South (Stevens - Gardens By The Bay) TE11 - TE22 except TE10 & TE21

23 June 2024: 7 stations opened (Tanjong Rhu - Bayshore) TE23 - TE29

Coming soon[]

2026: Opening of 2 stations (Bedok South & Sungei Bedok) TE30 & TE31

2027: Opening of Founders' Memorial station TE22A

2040: Replacing Changi Airport Branch Line (East-West Line) (Sungei Bedok - Tanah Merah) TE31 - TE? (NOTE:Changi Airport, Expo and Tanah Merah stations will no longer serve the Changi Airport Branch Line in 2040)

Future[]

Opening of Mount Pleasant and Marina South stations TE10 & TE21
